28/11/2002
ATHENS, Greece -- The government has decided to reduce ticket prices for the Summer Olympics in 2004, according to a press release issued Wednesday (27 November). 
Thus, prices will range from 10 to 300 euros, except for the opening and closing ceremonies. 
On average, ticket prices will be 34 per cent cheaper than those in the 2000 Summer Games in Sydney. 
(Athens News Agency, Macedonian Press Agency - 27/11/02)
